Sublime Text 3
   安装Package Contral        view->show console   粘贴 https://packagecontrol.io/installation#st3 
   Install Package :   SideBarEnhancements 
                       AutoPEP8     (CTRL+SHIFT+8)
                       Anaconda  
                                
   Anaconda 的配置：
            Setting-delfault   
                  "python_interpreter": "C:/Python36/python.exe"    (95行上下)
            setting-user
                  {"python_interpreter": "C:/Python36/python.exe",  
                  "complete_parameters": true ,
                  "complete_parameters": true ,  
                  "complete_parameters": true}
             Sublime Text 3\Packages\Python.sublime-settings   (配置python的.触发补全机制)  
                   {
                    "auto_complete_triggers":  [{"selector": "source.python - string - comment - constant.numeric", "characters": "."}]
                   }
   

                     
